    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2255440/extras/6b5df022b71d57209aefd30a4fbb1ab8.avif?t=1741191200\" width=584 height=76 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2255440/extras/bab8f1ff4143e096bbdbbe6a2e314079.poster.avif?t=1741191200\" width=600 height=248 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2255440/extras/bab8f1ff4143e096bbdbbe6a2e314079.webm?t=1741191200\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2255440/extras/bab8f1ff4143e096bbdbbe6a2e314079.mp4?t=1741191200\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Astrobit is a pixel art hero shooter where you create your own heroes. Experience a fast-paced online PvP space shooter with classic RPG elements. Explore different combinations of weapons, skills, abilities and perks every match to find awesome builds. Be a tanky heavy-hitter, a swift assassin, or go deep into magic to destroy your opponents. The choice is yours!<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Wishlist now, and secure your limited edition launch skin!</h2><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2255440/extras/b3db26feb015669e95db54f42ef6ba17.avif?t=1741191200\" width=584 height=76 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2255440/extras/dd5db4ac9da88fec5757e0772c855de4.poster.avif?t=1741191200\" width=600 height=284 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2255440/extras/dd5db4ac9da88fec5757e0772c855de4.webm?t=1741191200\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https